This paper is about link prediction for knowledge graphs, which is a task commonly studied in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), databases (cs.DB), and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of deep learning models, such as the multi-layer convolutional network introduced in this paper, is also a common theme in these sub-categories. Therefore, it is likely that this paper belongs to one or more of these sub-categories.
